Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:14.53,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,JC: Tonight, I do a skid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.65,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,JC: Richard steals some tyres.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:21.03,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And James get\Nkicked in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:28.62,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Sync and corrections by {\c&H00FFFF&}APOLLO{\c}\N{\c&H00FF00&} www.addic7ed.com{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:32.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello, thank you,\Nthank you everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:38.09,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get one thing\Nstraight, from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:41.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Formula 1 is better than NASCAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:43.04,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,CROWD CHEERS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:44.48,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It just is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:47.28,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,If you compare them, to\Nmusical instruments,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:52.32,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,F1 is a Stradivarius violin,\NNASCAR is banging a saucepan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:54.08,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,with a wooden spoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:57.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now, we all agree on that\Nin the civilised world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:00:59.56,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Well, when I say we all agree,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:06.16,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,we all agree apart from Richard\NJ Cheeseburger Hammond III.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:22.81,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,RH: I'm not alone in believing\Nin the supremacy of NASCAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:27.43,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's currently the most popular\Nspectator sport in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:32.61,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And there are many reasons why\Nit hits the spot with the fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:35.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The first is to do with its roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:43.31,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Unlike Formula 1, which began as\Na pastime for wealthy playboys
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:49.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and aristocrats, NASCAR has very\Nhumble, blue-collar origins.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:52.20,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,NASCAR has its roots back in the 1940s,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:55.70,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,when the Moonshine runners,\Nbasically naughty hicks,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:58.23,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,smuggling illegal booze\Nacross county lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:01.89,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,would modify their cars\Nto out run the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.84,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,One thing sort of led to another,\Nand before you knew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:08.05,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,they were holding informal\Nrace meetings in the evenings,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:12.20,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,on impromptu racetracks that they\Nkicked into the dirt in fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:18.47,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The cars the Moonshine runners\Nfavoured were ones like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:21.61,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,a respectable looking\N1941 Ford Business Coupe,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.65,0:02:27.48,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,which wouldn't raise the\Nsuspicions of a passing policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:29.47,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Clearly, the man in such a car as this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:33.26,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,is a man going about his business,\Nwhy would the cops disturb him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:36.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Underneath though is a\Nhighly-tuned engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:39.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,beefed up suspension, and\Ninside, a special hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:45.36,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,for the illegal booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:49.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Moonshine runners used this actual car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:53.16,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It smuggled hooky booze\Nacross county lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:58.25,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and then went on to race in\NNASCAR, it's the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:01.65,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,As the decades passed, the sport grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:04.90,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,'One critical time when trouble\Ncould be mighty contagious.'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:15.19,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,in NASCAR racing, but\Nthe drivers thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:18.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,well, the added weight was a\Nbit wussy, having a roll cage,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:22.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,so they just fitted them with things...\Nthat looked like roll cages,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:25.81,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,made out of off cuts of wood, say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:35.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Another reason I prefer this sport,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:39.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,apart from its rebellious streak,\Nis that next to the spaceships
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:44.11,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,you get F1, NASCAR machines\Nare beautifully simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:50.10,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,As was explained to me on\Nrace day at Texas Speedway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.04,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This is making 800 horsepower?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Closer to 900, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:55.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,900 horsepower. 900 horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:04:00.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And no electronic aids on this?\NNo. It literally carburetted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:03.81,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,NASCAR wants the drivers to\Nseparate themselves on the track,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:06.00,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,so, for myself, without having data,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:09.04,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I have to explain all the\Nsensations I feel in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:13.05,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Talk about spring changes, shot\Nchanges, geometry changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:15.29,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So, they're not downloading\Nit off a laptop?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:18.49,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,We don't even have a\Nfuel sensor in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:21.02,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And these little things,\Nthese are the ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:23.83,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's just to create some drag\Nwhen the car spins around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:25.77,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's not going to stop you flipping!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They've proven in the\Nwind tunnel that it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.88,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now, what really helps is this.\NThese deploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:34.60,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,When there's a low-pressure\Narea on the top, these deploy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and help set the car down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:39.72,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That stops you. Two on top.\NYou have these here, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:44.89,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's high-tech, that's like\Na-Land Rover's air vents at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.94,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's not mega high-tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:52.09,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,If you're a Formula 1 fan,\Nand a NASCAR cynic,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:56.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I think I know exactly what you'd\Nbe... saying if you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:59.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This looks, well, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:03.81,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You just keep your foot\Ndown, keep turning left,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and that's kind of it, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:09.35,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Whereas in Formula 1, there's\Ncorners and stuff to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So, do these drivers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.28,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,who can earn up to £15 million a year
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:19.71,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,have an easier time of\Nit than F1 drivers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:23.25,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Well, let's ask a man who's\Nraced in both sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:26.32,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,To drive? I would say there's nothing\Ndrives like a Formula 1 car,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.29,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,but these are more unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:31.49,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They slide around a lot,\Nthey have no breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:35.70,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I mean, when I tell you NO breaks,\Nbecause the car's so heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:37.70,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and the brakes are so tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:44.11,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I've got to say, ovals, I\Nthink, are more challenging,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:47.20,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and it's because the corner\Nstarts way over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and ends way over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.47,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And is the car moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:55.87,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The car's moving all the\Ntime, it's never settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:59.43,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And then, you take the cars all\Naround you, the turbulent air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:03.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,If they are on the outside of\Nyou, it's pulling you around,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:06.03,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,if they're in front of you,\Nyou just don't have the grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:10.89,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's when the entertainment\Nvalue... goes up tremendously,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:14.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because you're averaging\Nover 190 miles an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:16.68,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,with that many cars inches\Naway from one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:19.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and we'll be three or four\Nwide through these corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:24.71,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You go to Silverstone, you sit in\Na... stand on and you go, "meooooo."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.89,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You wait one half minutes.\NSee if the order has changed. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:29.53,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,But, most likely, it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.93,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They used to give awards because,\Noh, the overtaker of the year,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.39,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,you passed three people in\Nthe whole freaking year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:40.15,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So, lots of close racing in\Ncars that are tricky to drive,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:44.41,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,which means, as a bonus,\Nyou get lots of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's a contact sport, put it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:03.56,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,A lot of times, the contact that's\Nmade is either out of frustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.62,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,the guy wants to get another\Nguy out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:07.82,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You can't just ram him\Nbecause you can't overtake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.98,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,If you have bumpers, you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:12.78,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And when there is a coming together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:16.84,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,NASCAR drivers don't bother\Nsettling... with a stewards' enquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:19.68,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Let's see if they'll fight?\NHarvick's really mad at Montoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:22.71,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Have got a fight breaking out?\NHere it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:26.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,He's slowing back here, and we're\Ngoing to have a little talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:30.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This, too, is a bonus\Nfor the hard-core fans,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:33.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,who are not often mistaken\Nfor Harvard professors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:37.27,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:43.15,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,On race weekends, their main\Ndiet is beer and red meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:47.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,What if you were spotted eating a salad.\NEating salad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:51.68,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And they get a lot more\Naccess than F1 fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:56.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,These are actual fans\Nbeing driven around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:58.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,These are fans who have lined up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:01.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,that have paid to go around the\Ntrack with a professional,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.81,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,or some kind of driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:05.39,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine that in F1?\NIf you can do this, I'm coming tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:08.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They're in a pack of cars,\Nthey're not even on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:11.00,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Look at this, these are\Njust spectators, you or me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:20.55,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I didn't see how I might get the\Nsame chance to drive on that oval,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:23.29,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,but then I was told to report\Nto the drivers' briefing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:24.96,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,where I was in for a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:27.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,From the United States Air Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:31.20,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,four-star general, General Mark A\NWells III and his wife Betty Welsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:37.68,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,RAPTUROUS APPLAUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:41.64,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,From Top Gear UK, today's\Nhonorary pace car driver,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.63,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,from Birmingham England,\NRichard Hammond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:45.67,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,MUTED APPLAUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.19,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Race time arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.75,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,After the national anthem had finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:10.31,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,the man with the jetpack had landed...\Nand the B...52 bomber had flown past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:19.61,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It was time to me to lead the grid of\N43 cars out on the formation lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:24.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They are still coming,\Nthere's millions of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:27.52,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,ENGINES ROARS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:31.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Don't stall, Hammond, don't mess it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:37.59,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Behind me, 39,000 horsepower\Nwas itching to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:42.91,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I daren't look in the mirror, it's\Nlike being attacked by Tigers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:50.17,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Woah-ho-ho! Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:53.67,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,'Slip road is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:56.93,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,'Green flag.'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:03.29,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,We started that! We did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:13.22,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And my treats weren't over,\Nbecause I would be spending
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.99,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,the actual race helping\None of the teams,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:19.38,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,who gave me a very important job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:27.59,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm with the team.\NComing through, oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:31.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now, I will admit the one\Nproblem with NASCAR races
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.46,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,is that they're over 500 laps long,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:37.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,so at this point there is\Nonly one thing we can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:41.27,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,♪ We're gonna need a montage Montage
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:44.52,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,♪ Oh, it takes a montage Montage
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:47.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,♪ Show a lot of things Happening at once
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,♪ Remind everyone of what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:53.63,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,♪ That's called a montage Montage
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:57.08,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,♪ Oh, we want montage Montage
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:11:02.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,♪ Always fade out in a montage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:04.10,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,♪ If you fade out... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:08.90,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That did the trick, and 530 laps\Nlater, we had ourselves a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:14.11,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Three hours and 20 minutes\Nof racing just flew by,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:17.68,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,there's a man over there who won,\Nhe's now firing six guns in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:20.18,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,wearing his new Stetson.\NAnd he's delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:24.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now the whole circus moves on to the\Nnext place, to do it all again,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:27.19,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and there's a big argument\Nhere to say this is proof
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:31.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,F1 is po-faced, it could\Nlearn a lot from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:36.99,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The next morning, at a\Ndeserted Texas Speedway,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:40.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,there was one final treat in store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:47.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This. Plus a driving lesson\Nfrom NASCAR royalty Kyle Petty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:51.59,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel like anything\Nelse I've ever driven, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:54.77,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,this thing does not want\Nto go in a straight line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.20,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The car only wants to turn left,\Nit doesn't want to go straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.62,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Hit the grass, you've got\Nto run through the grass,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:02.27,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,it's like mowing the yard, you\Nhave to hit the grass. Hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:05.75,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,RICHARD SCREAMS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:10.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all the way down. I am so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:15.27,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,More gas, more gas, more gas, more gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:17.09,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:20.65,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Put her next to the wall little bit.\NI am next to the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:24.00,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,'Eventually, Kyle let\Nme go out on my own.'
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:31.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Letting it find grip.\NTrying not to fight it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:37.68,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's not just a big loop, it's\Ncomplex, it's three-dimensional,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:42.71,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and I'm wrestling my way around\Nit in a huge shouting dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:46.33,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I'm going to roll out of this\Ncorner... onto the straight now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:49.83,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,here I go, getting on the gas! Haha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.03,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:55.27,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I'm in an explosion again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:57.58,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,SCREAMS MANICALLY
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:12:59.88,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Where's it finding the grip?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:05.15,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Most of my lungs are on the\Nsame side, that's not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:08.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,'And then, just to add\Nto my problems... '
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:12.08,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, that's not what I\Nwanted to see in the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.72,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,that's too authentic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:21.77,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I don't need that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:29.62,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Arghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.49,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,CHEERING AND APPLAUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:34.93,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable. It was brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.78,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I loved it. It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.71,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:46.18,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,All right, OK, let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:50.96,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Come on then, Mr F1 Fan, I'm braced\Nand ready for your comments. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:54.74,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I agree with you. Eh?\NI do agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:59.84,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The Americans are very bad at some\Nthings, they can't say aluminium,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:02.27,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and they can't win a\Nwar without our help,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:06.95,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,but they are very good\Nat making dreary sports
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.03,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,very exciting to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:12.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Let's just take, for an\Nexample, rounders. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:15.08,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's played by small\Nchildren here, over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,it's Babe Ruth, and a religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:20.33,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Then you've got netball which\Nhere is schoolgirls standing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:24.00,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,so you can only move one foot, and\Nthere's four parents watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:27.12,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and over there it's, what is it?\NHarlem Globetrotters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:29.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They are quite easily amused.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:31.18,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Unbelievably easily\Namused, and that's why
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.25,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,they're able to make\NNASCAR exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:36.38,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's just some good ol' boys going\Nround in a circle. And they go,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"Oh, hell, I'll go pay to watch that."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:42.76,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,250,000 people turn up to watch it.\NBecause it is a good sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:46.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I mean Hammond you would say that,\Nbecause you're an American.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:49.28,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:54.39,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You've got a Stetson, cowboy boots,\Nchaps, a Harley-Davidson, a Mustang,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:56.61,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,you like to get a beer and you\Nput cheese on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:58.70,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I don't! I'm not American.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:01.15,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You have made a living out\Nof being... an American.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:03.11,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Your Saturday night programme is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:05.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,a fat man falling off some foam rubber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:08.02,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"Oh, right, hey, we'll watch that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.94,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Then they turn up in their millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.19,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,APPLAUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:17.20,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,JAMES HUMS STAR SPANGLED BANNER
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:19.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I'm not an American.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:25.20,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Look, Hammond, I wish the\NAmericans... ran a decent sport,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:29.73,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,if they got Formula 1, it would be\Nfantastic, because they would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:32.55,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"Let's have sprinklers\Ncoming on at random points
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.35,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"during the race," and\Nthat would be fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:35.75,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,There would be no more\Nstewards' enquiries,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.22,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and there will be no more of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:40.82,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"You've got a ten second drive-by\Npenalty," which ruins the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:43.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They would say, "Hamilton and\NMasa... you don't get on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:44.94,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,after the race, in your boxes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:46.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"on the winner's podium, slug it out."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:49.05,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'd watch that,\Nwould you watch that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.88,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I'd watch that. It would be brilliant.\NI would watch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we must do the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:56.48,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,We are starting with the\NInstitute of Advanced Motorists,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:57.73,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,you know the ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.61,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:02.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They are the ones who...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:05.29,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They say that you mustn't cross\Nhands on the steering wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:07.61,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You've got to shuffle it, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.33,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Never drive one-handed,\Nthey don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They prefer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:15.11,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Is anyone here in The Institute\Nof Advanced Motorists?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:17.04,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Like you are going to confess it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:19.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You are! So you are in the Institute?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.11,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So, you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:23.11,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Did you drive down...\Nhere today like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:30.41,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You're a passenger?\NOh, you can knock yourself out, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:41.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The Institute of Advanced Motorists...\Nhas launched a new thing called,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.63,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Drive And Survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,What, rather than Drive And Die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.73,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That would never work.\NDrive And Survive, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.38,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The idea is, what they've got is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,every week they're\Noffering motoring tips.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:55.67,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yes, so this week it's parking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.79,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a couple of examples\Nthey've come up with, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.55,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"Park on the left-hand side\Nof the road if possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.14,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"and always at night."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:09.23,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Eh? What happens if you\Narrive at lunch time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:12.99,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I parked here this morning.\NYou didn't! I did. You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:15.95,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Park always at night.\NAnother one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:18.14,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This is one I really can't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:21.63,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"When parking, open your\Nwindow in car parks,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:25.64,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"and turn off your stereo.\NYou can often hear something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:27.88,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"before you can see it."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:33.86,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,What, a lamppost? Lampposts actually\Nmake a very soft cooing sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:36.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:40.51,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I once heard a squelching\Nsound, and then a pop,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:43.23,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,but that was the neighbour's cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:45.84,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Can we move on? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.71,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I have some news, there is a new\NDodge Viper being announced,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:51.67,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and apparently it's going to employ\NFiat technology on it, which is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.57,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They mean is there's a new one,\Nand it won't work properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.27,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They haven't said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:58.28,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I suspect that Dodge\Nare a little worried
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.78,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,about the styling they have chosen,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:02.26,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because this is the\Nphotograph they have sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:05.14,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Doesn't tell you much, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:08.17,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Doesn't tell you a lot. Maybe it's shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:13.11,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Hey, now, you know sometimes\Nyou meet someone who has
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:16.15,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,a growth on their face, and it's\Nactually bigger than their face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:18.72,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:21.25,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No, I mean... one of those\Nreally ugly things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:26.00,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No, this is just a face, I'm talking\Nabout a growth. That's your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:30.74,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I bring this up, because\Nthere's a company in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.81,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,whose obviously used this growth thing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:36.14,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,as an inspiration for their\Nnew Prius campervan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:38.57,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Here it is. Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:41.23,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's the elephant car. It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:44.31,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,SLURS SPEECH: I'm so\Npleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:48.90,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I hope nobody knocks my trailer over.\NIt's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:51.75,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You've got a double bed in the\Nand another one in that growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:54.61,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That is not a car that you\Ncould talk to at a party,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:56.76,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,unless you are looking\Nat something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:00.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I've got news from Renault,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:01.71,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,they've got a new car, I've\Ngot a picture of it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:05.09,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,it's called the Influenza. Is it?\NIt isn't called the Influenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.66,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Well, it's something a bit like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:10.07,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's electric, as you can, because\Nthere it is plugged in, recharging.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:13.59,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I was wondering, when in the future,\Nwhen we're all driving electric cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:16.43,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,the cities are full of\Nthese charging points,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:19.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,won't ten-year-old boys go\Naround unplugging cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:21.75,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's what we would have\Ndone when I was ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:25.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Do you have to be ten, why wouldn't...\Nyou do that aged, I don't know, 52?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:28.71,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Well, quite.\NYou would know though... wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:32.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,If you saw somebody parked, you\Nwould just go... You would.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:35.08,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't. Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:38.58,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Remember the early Fiat Panda, the\Nboxy one that Giugiaro designed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:41.07,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,whenever I walk past one of\Nthose with a group of friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,we always picked it up\Nand turned it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:46.11,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You could just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:48.15,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I was going that way,\Nhow is that happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:50.19,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,In the same way as it's always great fun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:53.27,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,to lock someone else's bicycle\Nup with your bicycle lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:55.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You're just a yobbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:57.43,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Come on, Hammond, you\Nmust have done that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:20:00.91,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Or throw a brick through their\Nwindow, or set fire to their shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:05.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,If you go to Halfords, you buy a whole\Nload of really cheap bicycle locks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:08.78,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The combination ones... Then go along\Nthe street, locking people's bikes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:11.63,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Why would you do that?\NBecause it's funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:13.27,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No, it is, because you do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:17.15,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and I did this with Robert\NCook on York station, in 1978,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:19.65,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,if it was your bicycle,\Nyou'll know it was us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:22.59,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You lock it, hide behind some bins,\NWait for them to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:25.07,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They take their lock off,\N"Yes, my bicycle's good,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.90,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and they go off and go,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:30.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"I didn't put that on there.\N"People are watching, getting ideas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:34.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Don't do this, ten-year-olds and\N52-year-olds, we're not condoning this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.99,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,52-year-old children.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:39.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Or indeed unplugging\Npeoples' electric cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:44.19,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because when they come back and find\Nthe range says two, it's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:46.39,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It is funny.\NWe're not saying you should do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:48.55,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No, you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:50.74,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Were just saying you can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:55.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Last week we revealed that the\Npolice were claiming that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.65,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,driving under the influence\Nof a cold remedy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:00.29,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,is the same as driving under\Nthe influence of cocaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:01.93,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now, I drove down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:04.68,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because I got a cold that\NI haven't... mentioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:08.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I drove down here this morning\Nhaving taken some Day Nurse,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:10.21,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and I arrived without incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:13.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Did it make you very boring, and\Noverly confident at parties?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:17.31,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No, I'm always that, I was that anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:21.78,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So, I'm just letting you know that Day\NNurse and driving are OK. I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:25.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yeah, on that subject actually\Nlast week, you agreed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:27.68,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,in fact you challenged James\Nto do a lap of a track,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:31.03,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,you would be sewing on a button\Nat the same time as driving,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:33.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,he would be in a sleeping bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:35.62,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yes, and you would be\Ngiving yourself pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:41.49,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Those are the rules, so are we going...\Nto have our race? We did promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:47.47,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I've forgotten my sleeping bag, sir,\NI've been practising all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:53.28,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I promise we will do our sleeping\Nbag, sewing a button on,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:56.47,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and Hammond race before\Nthe end of the series.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.53,0:21:59.77,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Moving on, Mercedes SLS,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.20,0:22:03.39,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,James and Richard will tell you\Nthat it's too big and too stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:05.60,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It is. It is. No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:09.35,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It is a SUPERB car, and\Nas far as I'm concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:12.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,there is only one thing wrong with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:14.49,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,its doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.48,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That two things!\NWell, it is, it's too doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:18.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Hammond.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:24.47,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You might imagine, as you drive along
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:27.53,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,that people will think the\Ngullwing doors hark back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:31.63,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,to the magnificent 300 SL from 1954,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:36.27,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,but I suspect they won't\Nthink anything of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.57,0:22:41.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,What they will think, as you\Npull up and get out is,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:45.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"What a massive show off,"\Nand there's another problem
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.29,0:22:48.78,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,with gullwing doors as well\Nbecause if you roll the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.29,0:22:50.95,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,how do you open them to get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.00,0:22:54.87,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You're trapped in there, soaked\Nin petrol, burning, screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:22:58.86,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now, to prevent that from happening,\NMercedes has fitted the hinges
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:01.23,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,with explosive bolts that\Nare designed to fire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:03.08,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,if the car goes upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.73,0:23:06.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So, these doors then,\Nwhat they are are heavy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.13,0:23:09.81,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,unnecessary, embarrassing bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:14.52,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now however there is a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:20.51,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The SLS Roadster, a car which\Noffers all of the coupe's thrills,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:23.47,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,without leaving you purple-faced\Nwith embarrassment,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:25.47,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,every time you get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.39,0:23:30.66,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That is my idea of the perfect car.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:34.02,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,But it is quite difficult\Nto explain why.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:41.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,First of all, it costs as near as\Nmakes no difference, £200,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.49,0:23:46.03,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Which means it's in the same sort\Nof price bracket as a Rolls-Royce.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:49.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And with a Rolls-Royce you get more...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.44,0:23:52.64,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,car.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:24:00.19,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Of course, with this you get\Nthe magnificent jackhammer
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.10,0:24:03.99,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,50 cal, AMG soundtrack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:08.10,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,ENGINE REVS
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.14,0:24:14.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,But if that's all you want, why\Nnot buy a much cheaper C-Class?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.05,0:24:23.04,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This four-door saloon makes\Nexactly... the same sort of racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:24.94,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,ENGINE REVS
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.98,0:24:27.93,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,For around a quarter of the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.94,0:24:33.53,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Of course, you may say, "A-ha, I\Nlike being exposed to the elements."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.92,0:24:37.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I understand that, but I'll\Nlet you into a little secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.58,0:24:40.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,once you're doing 70 miles\Nan hour in a convertible,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.85,0:24:44.63,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,all you really notice is the\Nwind rushing through your hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.68,0:24:49.54,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,nothing about the car at all, the\Nwind is an all-consuming thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.36,0:24:54.04,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So, 70 miles an hour\Nfeels exactly the same
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.08,0:24:59.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,whether you're in this,\Nor this, or this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.01,0:25:04.75,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Let me put it this way, when\Nyou're... being attacked by a lion,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.79,0:25:08.93,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,it doesn't really matter whether\Nyou're in a bungalow or a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.08,0:25:13.25,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Being attacked by a\Nlion is the main thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.57,0:25:16.12,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Of course, at this point you may say,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.17,0:25:21.05,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"Yes, but I want a big V8\Nrear drive sports car."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.20,0:25:30.35,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So, what's wrong with this?\NThe big V8 rear drive Jaguar XKR.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.39,0:25:33.75,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's very similar to the\NMercedes, except that to my eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.79,0:25:38.46,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,it looks even better, and is\Nless than half the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.84,0:25:45.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Of course, you may think\Nthe SLS is more technical,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.46,0:25:49.04,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,more spectacular, and\Nthat's true, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.82,0:25:55.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The engine is a masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.29,0:25:59.41,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The seven speed, double clutch gearbox
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.45,0:26:02.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,is mounted at the back for\Nbetter weight distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.89,0:26:07.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's light. The prop shaft\Nis made from carbon fibre
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.05,0:26:09.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and only weighs four kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.73,0:26:11.84,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And all the little changes they've made
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.89,0:26:14.95,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,to the suspension on the\Nconvertible are so successful
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.98,0:26:18.57,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,they're applying them\Nto the coupe as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.20,0:26:24.43,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,However don't be fooled\Ninto thinking this is
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.46,0:26:27.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,some kind of track-munching\Ndriver's car...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.31,0:26:29.09,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,TYRES SQUEAL
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.13,0:26:33.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because, it isn't. Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.89,0:26:37.64,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Woah! God, strewth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.91,0:26:44.12,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It doesn't grip, steer, stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.20,0:26:47.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,or turn anything like\Nas well as a Ferrari.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.01,0:26:53.10,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Or an Aston Martin DBS, or even a BMW.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.14,0:26:55.03,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,HE LAUGHS
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.07,0:26:57.07,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,BMW M3.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.41,0:27:06.19,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You know what this is like,\Nan old American muscle car.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.23,0:27:10.78,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,A Dodge Charger with a\Nthree-pointed star on the nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.82,0:27:13.57,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You could almost call it crude.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.93,0:27:17.98,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So, there are many, many reasons\Nwhy you would not buy an SLS,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.01,0:27:21.09,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,but there's one why you would,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.13,0:27:23.61,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because it is fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.13,0:27:31.78,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Cars these days are\Nalso safe, and refined,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.82,0:27:35.18,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and they're all built in\Nwheat-free multi-ethnic factories,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.22,0:27:39.09,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,with one eye on Johnny polar\Nbear, but this just isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.13,0:27:47.20,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's just a gigantic,\Ntwo-fingered noisy salute
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.23,0:27:51.27,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,to the whole concept of\Nsustainable eco-ism.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.07,0:27:59.81,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's as in tune with the times\Nas a blaze at an oil refinery,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.85,0:28:02.16,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and I love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.20,0:28:05.09,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I also love the idiotically long bonnet,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.13,0:28:08.91,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and the 571 horsepowers\Nthat live beneath it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.95,0:28:11.46,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I love the speed of the roof, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.52,0:28:16.76,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You really can get it up or down at...\Na set of lights. I love its doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.01,0:28:19.19,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I love its windscreen wipers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.23,0:28:21.94,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I love the dust caps on the tyre valves.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.98,0:28:25.25,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I love the men who made\Nit, I love Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.29,0:28:28.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I want to move there, and\Nhave cold meat for breakfast,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.05,0:28:30.05,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and wear shorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.95,0:28:36.47,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I also love the way that in here,\Nit just feels like a Mercedes,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.23,0:28:38.66,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,apart from that, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.72,0:28:41.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And that, and that, and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.73,0:28:43.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I mean, apart from the launch control
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.01,0:28:46.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and all those buttons\Nthere it feels normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.38,0:28:51.91,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,There's no sense that you're in a\Nswivel-eyed destroyer of worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.63,0:28:57.53,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,There are many cars on the market today
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.53,0:29:00.99,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,for people who want to be sensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.03,0:29:06.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The SLS is rare because\Nit's for people who don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.03,0:29:14.04,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,CHEERING AND APPLAUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.08,0:29:19.02,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I like it, that's just...\NYou love this thing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.06,0:29:22.36,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's such a perfect car. It is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.42,0:29:24.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I can see why you love it,\Nlooking at you with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.96,0:29:28.84,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Think about it.\NIt's loud, old-fashioned, not sensible,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.88,0:29:31.55,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,it's got a hole in the top,\Nit's you, with a tax disc.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.59,0:29:33.53,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's what it is. Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.57,0:29:37.76,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And now, we must find out how\Nfast it goes round our track,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.07,0:29:40.53,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and that means handing it over\Nto our tame racing driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.82,0:29:43.64,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Some say that he's the\Nonly man in Britain
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.68,0:29:47.71,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,who knows what B&Q stands for.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.07,0:29:52.03,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And that he can't give his\Nmillion-pound bonus back
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.08,0:29:54.77,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because he's already spent it...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.81,0:29:56.74,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,on French breast implants.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.78,0:30:00.28,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,All we know is... he's called The Stig.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.32,0:30:06.15,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And he's off. Nice, clean\Nstart on this crisp, dry day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.35,0:30:08.46,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That is pure engine sound\Nyou're hearing, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.50,0:30:10.55,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No active exhaust valve\Nnonsense in the SLS.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.55,0:30:12.60,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,First corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.69,0:30:16.08,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,He's getting a bit sideways on\Nthe way out, but he's through!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.12,0:30:19.33,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,MUSIC: Theme tune from "The Archers"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.37,0:30:21.27,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I should explain,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.31,0:30:24.86,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,the Stig has become a massive\NArchers fan recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.90,0:30:27.83,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,He keeps it tidy through\NChicago down to Hammerhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.87,0:30:30.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This is a car that needs\Nvery precise driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.46,0:30:32.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Too violent with the\Nsteering, throttle or brakes
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.84,0:30:34.67,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and it will bite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.69,0:30:36.90,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Look at that. Beautifully done.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.93,0:30:38.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,VOICES FROM THE ARCHERS:\N'I'll be as quick as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.73,0:30:40.91,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,'I can help, if that'll\Nspeed things up.'
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.82,0:30:45.85,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Rural drivel there.\NUp the gears to Follow-Through
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.89,0:30:47.55,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,like all flappy-pedal boxers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.59,0:30:50.65,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Not so good in town, but\Nit works brilliantly here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.69,0:30:52.54,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,OK, he's passed the tyres.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.56,0:30:56.56,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Roadster is 40 kilos heavier than\Nthe Coupe, so will it be slower?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.60,0:30:59.58,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,We'll never know, because the\NCoupe has never been round here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.62,0:31:02.46,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's Gambon done and across the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.10,0:31:06.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.84,0:31:08.55,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.59,0:31:10.08,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No. Higher than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.12,0:31:14.20,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,1.19.6, so it's there,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.24,0:31:17.75,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,between the Lamborghini Gallardo\Nand a Ferrari Scuderia.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.81,0:31:20.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Not bad, but it's hardly\Nin the medals, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.73,0:31:24.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,What this is, it's like\NRobert Downey Jnr.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.01,0:31:28.14,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,He's never won an Oscar,\Nbut he's still brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.18,0:31:30.89,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Anyway...\NI've got no idea what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.96,0:31:32.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, you work it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.49,0:31:36.02,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because it is time to put a star\Nin our reasonably-priced car.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.06,0:31:40.58,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Is it Robert Downey Junior? No.\NBut he is an American, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.62,0:31:41.76,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.80,0:31:45.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, please\Nwelcome Matt Le Blanc!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.96,0:31:51.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,CHEERING AND APPLAUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.93,0:31:55.53,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Have a seat. He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.61,0:32:02.72,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's a good welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.76,0:32:04.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now, first of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.46,0:32:06.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,hearty congratulations\Non your Golden Globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.06,0:32:07.65,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Last week, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.70,0:32:10.98,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Last week or the week before,\NI don't know, I had to fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.02,0:32:13.16,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I came back here after Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.20,0:32:17.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Is it easier to win an award or lose one
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.29,0:32:19.49,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,in terms of getting your face right?\NI'm never quite sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.53,0:32:23.12,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,If you win, you've got to\Nlook proud, but not smug,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.16,0:32:25.14,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and that's a tricky thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.21,0:32:27.57,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I've got a lot of practice\Nat the losing face.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.57,0:32:29.93,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The losing face? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.97,0:32:32.18,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The camera sits at your\Ntable and stays on you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.22,0:32:34.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and the guy's halfway through his speech
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.38,0:32:36.47,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and they still have a\Ncamera on you... so you...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.51,0:32:38.32,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,LAUGHTER
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.36,0:32:39.93,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,He deserved it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.97,0:32:43.73,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,We lost spectacularly last week to\Na programme called This Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.80,0:32:46.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You know this? No. It's a programme...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.53,0:32:48.62,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Fix! Fix!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.66,0:32:53.16,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Well, no, it's a programme where men\Nput their fingers in other men.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.20,0:32:55.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,LAUGHTER
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.84,0:32:59.70,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They did! And as a result of that,\Nwe were blown out of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.78,0:33:03.36,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The viewing public likes that more.\NSo well done, This Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.82,0:33:08.91,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You won your Golden Globe for Episodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.95,0:33:10.95,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I don't know if anybody\Nhere has seen Episodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.04,0:33:13.36,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I think it is just brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.41,0:33:15.76,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NYou've just done the second series,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.82,0:33:18.43,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,which is why you're here.\NWe finished a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.50,0:33:20.04,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Talk us through the plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.08,0:33:21.95,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Because of those of you\Nwho have not seen yet
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.02,0:33:25.77,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,OK, it's a show about a fictitious\Nshow that starts in the UK
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.89,0:33:30.64,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and it's bought by the American networks\Nto be revamped and remade in the States.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.76,0:33:34.00,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,They promise them the\Nworld and one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.18,0:33:36.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,every promise is broken, including\Nthe fact that they keep
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.83,0:33:40.90,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,their lead actor played by Richard\NGriffiths and they tell him,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.93,0:33:44.04,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"No, can't have him.\NYou're going to hire a Matt Le Blanc."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.45,0:33:47.91,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So I play this weird,\Nbizarre version of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.92,0:33:52.87,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Of course, Episodes has not\Nyet become the huge hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.92,0:33:55.77,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,What you're best known for is...\NWell, I tell you what,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.81,0:33:58.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,let's show you a clip of you\Nin your best role. Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.78,0:34:03.33,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This is Bob Seger, obviously.\NNight Moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.44,0:34:07.84,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This was the video shot in 1994,\Nand if we look very carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.02,0:34:13.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,here's the heroine and... whoa!\NWait a minute! Who is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.45,0:34:20.66,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That was '94.\NFriends had already started in '94,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.70,0:34:23.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,so you were moonlighting\Nin Seger videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.17,0:34:25.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,A friend of mine directed\Nthat and he called me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.54,0:34:28.94,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and said, "Hey, I'm doing a video\Nfor Bob Seger for Night Moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.98,0:34:31.98,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"Do you want to be the hero guy?\N" And I said, "Sure, yeah."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.02,0:34:36.25,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So I go down there and they get in\Nthe little trailer to get ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.30,0:34:39.62,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,we're at this drive-in theatre,\Nand someone knocks on the door
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.70,0:34:41.98,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and says, "Bob Seger would like\Nto see you in his motor home."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.05,0:34:46.78,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So I go over and I go into the motor\Nhome and he starts talking me through
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.83,0:34:49.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,what it was like when he was\Nyoung and going to the drive-in
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.48,0:34:53.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and trying to pick up girls and he\Nbreaks out a bottle of tequila.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.17,0:34:56.49,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Next thing I know, we down\Na whole bottle of tequila,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.55,0:34:58.76,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Bob Seger and I, and then\Nthey knock on the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.81,0:35:02.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"Ready for you on set!\N" So I'm drunk in the whole video.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.98,0:35:04.55,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And it wasn't just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.60,0:35:07.16,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You were also in a Tom Petty video.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.28,0:35:09.78,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Drunk in that one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.82,0:35:12.86,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Drunk today? Hmm, yeah. A little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.35,0:35:18.82,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now, cars. I know you are\Nwhat we call a petrol head,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.89,0:35:21.30,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I think you call a gear head.\NWe know this...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.35,0:35:23.16,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I've got an inkling of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.20,0:35:25.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because when I was watching Episodes,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.73,0:35:28.30,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,we've got a clip here which\Ngives us a bit of an insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.34,0:35:29.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Let's just run this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.01,0:35:32.31,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Tell me that's not yours! You like?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.69,0:35:34.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.27,0:35:37.67,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I read there was only three\Nin the whole world. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.18,0:35:41.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Me, the Sultan of Brunei\Nand some drug guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.01,0:35:43.83,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.97,0:35:45.32,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.22,0:35:50.73,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And that's while I was never picked.\NReally? Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.86,0:35:54.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I am SO happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.54,0:35:56.66,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.07,0:35:59.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.00,0:36:01.62,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.80,0:36:04.11,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Get a room! Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.58,0:36:06.63,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I wish I knew how to drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.21,0:36:15.81,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's an Alfa 8C convertible.\NThat's a very rare car.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.85,0:36:18.72,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You end up in an XK\Nin that first series.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.76,0:36:21.32,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Right. That was a funny story\Nabout that car because
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.36,0:36:25.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,when they agree to let us use it in\Nthe show, it hadn't been sold yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.06,0:36:27.46,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,By the time we needed it,\Nsomeone had bought it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.56,0:36:30.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,so it showed up with its own\Nsecurity team and everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.97,0:36:34.74,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I got to drive it maybe five feet.\NYOU did? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.80,0:36:37.23,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Steve drove it further than I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.46,0:36:41.90,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This year, it's Ron Dennis's\Npersonal Mercedes SLR he loaned us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.01,0:36:45.00,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,What was that like?\NI didn't get to drive that one either!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.54,0:36:49.96,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You're the only one crazy enough to let\Nme behind the wheel, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.05,0:36:55.49,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now, your car history is chequered,\NIsn't it? At best, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.60,0:36:58.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You had an Audi 5000,\Nwhich we'd call 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.55,0:37:01.66,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That was the one that had the\Nunintended acceleration stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.70,0:37:04.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yeah, not the one I had,\Nbut I heard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.96,0:37:06.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It was like a crap shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.73,0:37:10.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And then there was a\NFiat X1/9 that came,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.84,0:37:13.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,which is like a motorised vajazzle,\NI always think, the X1/9.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.42,0:37:18.20,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was probably a mistake.\NI bought it at a used car lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.24,0:37:21.41,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I was driving by and, you know, "Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.45,0:37:24.00,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"That looks like a good waste\Nof money right there."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.04,0:37:26.98,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You used to have a Porsche\NTurbo, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.02,0:37:30.54,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I had a 2000 996 turbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.58,0:37:32.73,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,As I understand it, you modified that,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.78,0:37:36.21,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,cos when we buy cars in\NEurope, BMWs or Porsches
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.24,0:37:39.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,or whatever they might be,\Nthat's what they're like,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.17,0:37:40.48,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,whereas in the States,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.52,0:37:43.72,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,there seems to be a culture of you\Nbuy a car and then you take it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.76,0:37:46.48,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,to a shop and somebody tweaks\Nit and fiddles with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.52,0:37:50.28,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Right. Is that something you\Njust feel you have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.32,0:37:54.53,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Well, for me, it's like, if someone who\Ndoesn't know anything about cars
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.60,0:37:57.53,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,can just go down to the\Nstore and get the same car,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.59,0:37:59.23,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.27,0:38:03.03,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I mean, I love cars, so I should\Ngo a LITTLE faster, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.11,0:38:04.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So what did you do to the Turbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.73,0:38:08.76,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The Turbo, I had a Gemballa\Ncomputer programme put in it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.80,0:38:11.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and an exhaust and TechArt suspension.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.73,0:38:16.31,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Then I took it in to have the mass\Nair sensor was starting to...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.41,0:38:18.76,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This is probably super-boring\Nfor most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.80,0:38:22.16,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No, it's Top Gear, for once you're\Nallowed to talk about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.20,0:38:25.07,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The Tonight Show wouldn't let\Nme talk about any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.11,0:38:27.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Are you a man who goes\Nand drives on circuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.14,0:38:31.16,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Occasionally, yeah,\Nmostly with the bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.24,0:38:34.56,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I know that's a sore subject with you.\NNo, you can talk about bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.62,0:38:36.20,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You've got three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.45,0:38:39.41,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And they're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.45,0:38:41.94,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So, have you ever driven\Nround Laguna Seca,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.98,0:38:44.10,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,which is your nearest track, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.14,0:38:47.26,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Willow Springs is probably closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.30,0:38:49.29,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,but Laguna Seca is such a\Nbeautiful facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.29,0:38:51.28,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You know, the Corkscrew there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.32,0:38:54.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The Corkscrew is a corner\Nthat I just find impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.48,0:38:56.28,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,to get round without crashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.32,0:39:01.20,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Six stories I think it drops.\NIt's left, right, it's six stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.25,0:39:04.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not my idea of fun.\NOur track is much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.67,0:39:07.95,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I know you took your trip\Ndown here quite seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.01,0:39:11.08,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because you told our researcher,\Nyou were asking about the Kia
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.12,0:39:14.43,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and the roll cage, which you said,\N"Ah, that'll make it more rigid."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.54,0:39:18.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,We've never had any of this before\Nfrom a guest, somebody that keen on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.58,0:39:20.67,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's probably the best\Nhandling Kia there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.77,0:39:24.86,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Pretty nice little car.\NWho here would like to see Matt's lap?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.45,0:39:28.98,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE CHEERS IN ASSENT\NMe too, yeah!\NLet's have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.20,0:39:36.66,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Just don't use the brake\Nas much, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.70,0:39:39.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No, you're going to\Nneed the brakes there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.17,0:39:41.66,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Were you OK with having a\Nstick-shift on your left?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.70,0:39:44.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I missed a couple of\Nshifts here and there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.48,0:39:48.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Well, that looks, that's the sort\Nof tidy corner. Sloppy at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.54,0:39:51.04,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,We're keeping it the tidy through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.08,0:39:54.00,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The more boring it looks,\Nthe faster it often is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.04,0:39:58.08,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's, well, very boring indeed\Nthrough there. Hammerhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.12,0:40:03.22,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Almost got the front wheel off\Nthe ground there, but not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.26,0:40:06.57,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's very tight on the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.67,0:40:12.20,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Matt whisting{\b}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.26,0:40:15.41,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It was obviously boring you\Nto death as well out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.50,0:40:18.96,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Flat through there, yeah, no lifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.54,0:40:25.08,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Your heart is beating\Nonce every three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.12,0:40:31.41,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You're going to cut this one.\NYeah... that's very cut. Gambon, cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.45,0:40:35.14,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, very cut.\NAnd there we are, across the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.42,0:40:45.32,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,What do you reckon? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.36,0:40:47.70,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Well, hopefully in the\Ntop half somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.70,0:40:50.04,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Hopefully in the top half.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.08,0:40:54.35,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Well, often when laps look\Nthat drama-less, as it were,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.39,0:40:56.07,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,they can be quite fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.11,0:41:00.87,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So there's the board.\NRowan Atkinson currently leading 1.42.2.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.91,0:41:04.41,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's quick.\NYes, 1.42.2 is unbelievably quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.48,0:41:07.54,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Halfway would put you\Nwith Bob Geldof, 1.48.1.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.54,0:41:12.32,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You did it, Matt Le\NBlanc, in one minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.32,0:41:16.60,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,40...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.88,0:41:19.16,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,two...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.20,0:41:21.10,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,AUDIENCE GASPS
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.14,0:41:22.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.17,0:41:24.77,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,RAPTUROUS CHEERING
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.77,0:41:33.98,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Fastest ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.08,0:41:39.07,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Fastest ever! That's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.58,0:41:47.52,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I just knew when I started...\NAre you serious? Absolutely serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.60,0:41:51.60,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You were apparently running at\N1.42.2, absolutely level with Rowan,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.66,0:41:53.53,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,who, by the way, has just hung himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.57,0:41:57.56,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and then on the last lap,\Npopped in at 1.42.1. Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.65,0:41:59.48,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So there we are, ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.52,0:42:02.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,the fastest guest we've ever had.\NMatt Le Blanc!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.01,0:42:06.60,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.64,0:42:08.89,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.36,0:42:14.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now, we may be in a spot of\Neconomic bother at the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.54,0:42:18.84,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,however, Rolls-Royce, Bentley and\NAston Martin are all enjoying
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.88,0:42:22.85,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,record sales, and all because\Nof demand from China.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.17,0:42:27.25,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The thing is, though, that people with\Nadenoids are saying in five years' time,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.31,0:42:29.41,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,the Chinese are going\Nto stop buying our cars
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.45,0:42:31.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and WE will start buying theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.01,0:42:33.98,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,In fact, if I had a pound\Nfor everyone who said,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.04,0:42:39.15,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"Soon you will be driving a Chinese car\N," I'd be able to afford a Chinese car.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.42,0:42:43.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,To see if they have a point, Jeremy\Nand I decided to pop over to
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.01,0:42:46.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Beijing and find out what\Nall the fuss is about.\N[Back ground music : Brian Eno - Passing Over starts playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.16,0:42:58.72,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,For the last 50 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.76,0:43:01.74,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,there have been two types\Nof transport in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.78,0:43:06.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,If you were Chairman Mao, you had\Na honky, red-flag armoured limo.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.81,0:43:10.33,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,If you were not Chairman\NMao, you had one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.52,0:43:15.87,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Or if you were really lucky,\Nyou had one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.03,0:43:18.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Even in the early '90s,\Nthe idea that you would
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.73,0:43:21.58,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,own a car was complete madness,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.62,0:43:23.96,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because you'd never have\Nbeen able to afford it,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.00,0:43:27.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and even if you could afford it,\Nyou weren't allowed to have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.01,0:43:30.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now, though, things have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.28,0:43:43.75,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,In 1977, there were one\Nmillion cars in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.80,0:43:50.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,By 2008, there were 51 million.\NNow there are 85 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.44,0:43:54.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And every day that\Nnumber swells by 38,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.49,0:44:00.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Somebody buys a new car in\NChina every 2.3 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.67,0:44:05.63,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,To keep up with demand,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.67,0:44:09.36,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,China's car factories are\Nrunning at light speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.40,0:44:15.70,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Last year, the whole of Europe combined\Nproduced 16.9 million vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.74,0:44:20.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,China all on its own produced\N1.3 million more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.89,0:44:26.14,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And it's not just Chinese companies-\Nthat are cashing in on the boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.71,0:44:30.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Audi is now making long-wheelbase\Nversions of its cars
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.47,0:44:33.78,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,specifically for sale in\NChina and nowhere else,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.82,0:44:38.43,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because in China, space in the back-\Nmatters more than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.80,0:44:43.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,China is now the world's\Nsecond-biggest oil consumer,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.13,0:44:47.96,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,taking more barrels per day\Nthan India and Japan combined.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.74,0:44:52.62,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,By 2025, the road network\Nwill be big enough to cover
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.65,0:44:55.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,the whole of the British Isles...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.13,0:44:57.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,all of it, Scottish\NHighlands, the lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.98,0:45:00.75,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,20 times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.37,0:45:04.04,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So where did it all begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.08,0:45:08.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Well, one of the first cars ever\Nto be sold in China was this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.05,0:45:13.23,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The CA6410UA.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.48,0:45:17.14,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Better known to you and I\Nas the Austin Maestro.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.18,0:45:20.47,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's the\Nback end of a Maestro,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.51,0:45:25.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,but the front end of a Montego, and\Nit's powered by a Toyota engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.38,0:45:29.41,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The history behind this car\Nthough is even more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.92,0:45:36.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,In 1998, a Chinese tobacco\Ncompany bought the tooling
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.54,0:45:40.30,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,for the Maestro and the Montego\Nso they could be made in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.34,0:45:42.00,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,In order to make them in China,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.04,0:45:45.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,they had to tell the authorities\Nthat they were building buses.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.33,0:45:49.15,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This car... or I should say THESE cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.19,0:45:51.05,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because this is a bit\Nof a cut-and-shut job...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.16,0:45:54.21,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,these were terrible when they\Nwere being built in Britain,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.40,0:45:58.24,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,so imagine what they like when they\Nwere being made using worn-out tools
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.31,0:46:02.49,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,by a company that's the Chinese\Nequivalent of Player's No 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.65,0:46:04.26,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's just hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.03,0:46:14.35,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Pretty soon, various bright\Nsparks in China started to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.49,0:46:17.57,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Why buy the rights to\Nmake cars we don't want
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.68,0:46:20.25,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,when we can just copy\Nthe ones we DO want?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.43,0:46:25.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The Chinese are very good\Nat this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.10,0:46:28.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I'm speaking to you from\Nbehind a pair of fake Ray-Bans
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.38,0:46:32.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,wearing a fake Armani jacket,\Ncarrying a fate Louis Vuitton bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.84,0:46:36.70,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,in which we find a fake iPad
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.74,0:46:40.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and a fake iPhone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.62,0:46:42.94,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And if we consult my fake Omega,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.19,0:46:46.30,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,we see that it's 2.35. probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.48,0:46:49.96,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Which means it is time to pop into\Nthe fake Starbucks over there
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.00,0:46:52.30,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,for a cup of fake coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.34,0:46:56.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It seems, then, that the expression...\N"copyright infringement"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.05,0:47:00.11,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,doesn't translate terribly\Nwell into Mandarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.49,0:47:04.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,All of which explains this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.46,0:47:07.83,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It looks like a BMW X5,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.87,0:47:10.64,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,but actually, it's a blatant copy called
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.68,0:47:19.16,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,the Shuanhuan S-CEO HBJ6474Y.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.46,0:47:23.54,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Then there's this, a\Ncopy of the Fiat Panda.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.80,0:47:28.38,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And this, a copy of the Smart ForTwo.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.59,0:47:33.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And this, a copy of the Daewoo Matiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.46,0:47:35.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Did you hear about the\NLifan motorcycles?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.12,0:47:39.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Lifan is a Chinese company that make\Ncopies of small Honda motorcycles,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.20,0:47:44.30,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,but to make sure you don't notice,\Nthey change the name on the tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.47,0:47:49.30,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,To what? Hongda. H-O-N-G-D-A.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.36,0:47:52.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Hongda? So on that basis,\Nis this Mini a Minging?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.45,0:47:55.52,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It should be, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.60,0:47:59.90,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Because it is the most\Ntragic-looking thing. It's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.96,0:48:01.98,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's like somebody's\Ndescribed Mini to somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.98,0:48:04.00,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,on the telephone.\NOr sent a blurry fax.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.05,0:48:05.55,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"There we are, that's\Nwhat it looks like."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.61,0:48:07.63,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It is very cheap. How much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.93,0:48:10.21,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,£4,100. That is cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.32,0:48:14.10,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,But this Toyota Aygo over\Nhere is only£3,500.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.22,0:48:17.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's not a Aygo. That's an FO.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.41,0:48:21.15,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's what it's called. FO.\NI think that's a message to Toyota
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.29,0:48:25.11,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,if Toyota ever decide\Nto sue the fake makers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.15,0:48:27.16,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Do these people ever get taken to court?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.20,0:48:32.86,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yeah. BMW sued the people making\Nthe X5 fake and they lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.90,0:48:35.12,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Really? Yeah.\NThe Chinese government said,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.16,0:48:37.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"No, it doesn't look like\Nanything like an X5."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.41,0:48:40.14,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's funny, I thought they looked...\Nreally similar. No, they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.30,0:48:44.51,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Don't they? No. It's just me?\NNo, it's just you. Right. OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.20,0:48:47.56,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's easy to see why they were copying
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.61,0:48:52.46,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because when they tried to go it alone,\Nthe results weren't very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.43,0:49:01.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This tripod is the XF15OZK-4,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.54,0:49:04.83,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and naturally, we\Ncouldn't wait to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.87,0:49:06.54,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.58,0:49:08.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You see one yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.84,0:49:10.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.84,0:49:12.47,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,James!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.51,0:49:15.50,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,'On the plus side, we now\Nknew where the engine was,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.65,0:49:19.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,'information that came in handy\Nabout 20 seconds later.'
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.21,0:49:23.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,ENGINE STRUGGLES TO START
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.49,0:49:26.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.41,0:49:31.27,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,'After some local bodging, we\Nwere back in and on our way.'
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.27,0:49:39.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.44,0:49:42.54,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's reverse.\NThat's gone into nought, fifth, second.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.29,0:49:45.31,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,First, that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.30,0:49:47.90,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.51,0:49:52.73,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's going to look very\Nfunny from the outside, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.73,0:49:54.95,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now you're doing second.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.97,0:49:59.41,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,'Having mastered the gearbox,\Nit was time to open up
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.47,0:50:02.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,'the single-cylinder\N12-horsepower engine.'
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.62,0:50:10.31,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The acceleration is blinding!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.71,0:50:15.22,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's like a safety device.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.26,0:50:18.99,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,You accelerate too hard, your\Nfeet come off the pedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.18,0:50:26.71,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Hold on to your spine. Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.92,0:50:31.78,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,2004, this car was launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.82,0:50:33.32,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,If I'd shown this to\Nyou and asked you when
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.32,0:50:34.82,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,it was built, when\Nwould you have said?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.91,0:50:38.21,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,1957. I would say it was\Nolder than me. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.34,0:50:40.61,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.85,0:50:42.43,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Poor quality!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.32,0:50:44.64,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,BOTH: Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.68,0:50:49.28,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Come on, redeeming feature, James.\NThere must be a redeeming feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.32,0:50:53.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Er... It's character-building.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.68,0:50:57.52,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No, because I mean this... BOTH: Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.56,0:50:59.09,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,CARS HORNS BEEP
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.13,0:51:04.01,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,ENGINE STRUGGLES TO START
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.52,0:51:07.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I think our test drive's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.36,0:51:13.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So we moved on to look at some\Nmore modern Chinese cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.22,0:51:20.95,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This is the JACJ7.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.99,0:51:24.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,At the 6th annual Chinese\Ngovernment procurement conference,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.96,0:51:29.03,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,it won the highly coveted\Nfirst choice in middle class
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.07,0:51:31.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,of government procurement award.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.46,0:51:37.80,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And then there's the\NHaval M2 which is...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.30,0:51:41.85,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Well, we have absolutely\Nno idea what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.40,0:51:45.58,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Can I read you something\Nfrom the blurb? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.24,0:51:50.28,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,About the styling of the M2.\NI think this absolutely sums it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.36,0:51:54.67,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"Body on the side of the\Nlion to go straight fair
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.85,0:51:57.89,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,"with enough of the masculine\Nqualities of men."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.64,0:52:07.90,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,If we're honest, the M2 and\Nthe J7 aren't much good.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.64,0:52:14.40,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So, are there any\NChinese cars which are?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.05,0:52:21.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Well, this is a Guangzhou Trumpchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.36,0:52:26.59,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And it's not made from tin\Nfoil or bits of old Austin.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.71,0:52:34.61,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Underneath, it's an Alfa Romeo 166.\NThis might be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.71,0:52:42.46,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I think, however, that this\NRoewe 350 will be even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.32,0:52:47.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The Roewe 350 is particularly important,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.46,0:52:51.76,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,because it will eventually become\Nan MG in Britain, the MG 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.80,0:52:53.35,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It will be changed slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.44,0:52:55.59,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The engine will be different because
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.63,0:52:58.56,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,it needs to meet legislation\Nfor emissions, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.62,0:53:01.49,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,But basically, I'm driving\Na car that you will
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.57,0:53:03.77,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,be able to buy in Britain very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.08,0:53:11.48,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Essentially, then, what we have\Nhere is an Alfa Romeo and an MG.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.52,0:53:14.67,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Those, of course, are\Nvery sporting names,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.74,0:53:18.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and that's why we've come to\Nthis very picturesque racetrack.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.94,0:53:25.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,What we're going to do is see\Nwhich of these cars can set
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.52,0:53:29.02,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,the fastest lap time.\NWell, WE'RE not. No, we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.09,0:53:31.31,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,We're going to use our\Ntame racing driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.42,0:53:33.96,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Some say he's the Stig, but he isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.25,0:53:36.84,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,He is the Stig's Chinese cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.73,0:53:47.09,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Now, I should explain, driving\Nis his second favourite thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.14,0:53:50.57,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,What's his first favourite thing?\NAttacking people. He does it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.66,0:53:54.57,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,He's constantly at it.\NWhy are you doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.63,0:53:58.18,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go and do some driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.40,0:54:00.32,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Do some driving. Get into the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.36,0:54:02.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Stop attacking us! Get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.06,0:54:06.15,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No, he's got to get in the car.\NGet in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.24,0:54:09.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Trumpchi. Trumpchi.\NGet in the Trumpchi. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.95,0:54:15.14,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No, that's the director.\NThat's the director!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.39,0:54:19.84,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,What if I start the\Nengine, would that do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.96,0:54:23.17,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, in you go.\NThey bow, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.28,0:54:25.54,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Go in. Get in. Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.98,0:54:32.45,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's the worst Stig we've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.81,0:54:37.81,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,HE COUNTS DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.88,0:54:46.99,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Attack Stig doesn't attack\Nthe throttle, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.83,0:54:49.37,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Good-looking car, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.37,0:54:50.91,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It is a good-looking car,\Nit's growing on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.98,0:54:54.25,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's got the boot shape of\Nthe Lancia Gamma. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.40,0:54:58.94,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And it has an Alfa engine. Does it? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.82,0:55:04.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,But it is called a Trumpchi.\NIt is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.17,0:55:08.10,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That is quite funny.\NWhat are you driving these days, Jeremy?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.14,0:55:10.95,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Well, it's interesting...\Nunderneath, it's an Alfa.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.99,0:55:12.52,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It is a Trumpchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.76,0:55:19.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Attack Stig is back, everybody!\NWatch out! And across the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.88,0:55:21.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,1.50, dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.96,0:55:25.82,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,We've got to get him out of\Nthat car and into the Roewe.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.86,0:55:28.41,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Get him in the Roewe as\Nquickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.46,0:55:31.36,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Get him in the Roewe! It's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.40,0:55:32.66,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,He's attacking the starter.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.77,0:55:35.36,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a racist thing,\Nhe just didn't like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.86,0:55:41.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,He's coming towards us now. No.\NYou were good! 150 dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.70,0:55:46.14,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Eventually, Attack Stig was\Ncorralled into James's Roewe.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.65,0:55:52.34,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,HE COUNTS DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.93,0:55:55.06,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That begins quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.99,0:55:59.57,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,How many horsepower has it got? 107.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.51,0:56:02.07,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That's a 1.5, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.04,0:56:06.32,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,How have they got so few horsepower?\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.63,0:56:10.30,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And I don't like to sound like you,\NBut that's not enough power.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.17,0:56:14.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Because they called it\NRoewe, because Roewe...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.17,0:56:16.26,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,BOTH: Is how they would say Rover.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.30,0:56:20.05,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I thought they'd say Lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.24,0:56:27.70,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The seconds ticked by, but\Nthere was no sign of my Roewe.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.74,0:56:29.91,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Where has he gone? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.30,0:56:37.48,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,After we dragged Attack\NStig off the marshal...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.51,0:56:39.03,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Across the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.07,0:56:41.73,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,We got a clean lap time for the Roewe.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.23,0:56:45.84,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Victory by one tenth of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.61,0:56:50.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,A fairly hollow victory, though, as...\Nwe estimate that on the same track
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.96,0:56:55.81,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,a comparable European car would\Nbe ten or 15 seconds faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.17,0:56:59.48,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So, what about safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.52,0:57:04.07,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Chinese crash tests are much the\Nsame as the ones we have in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.11,0:57:07.11,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,But the speeds are a bit lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.24,0:57:33.51,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Any injuries? None at all. Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.55,0:57:35.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Not a scratch. What about the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.42,0:57:38.93,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No damage at all. Really?\NNo. That's a pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.27,0:57:44.84,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.80,0:57:53.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,ELECTRONIC CHINESE VOICE
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.38,0:57:57.28,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Having satisfied ourselves\Nthat these cars
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.34,0:57:59.08,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,had been through all their crash tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.29,0:58:04.96,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,we were confident that we could take\Nthem onto the streets of Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.24,0:58:09.26,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This might not be as nice to drive,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.30,0:58:12.54,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,or as fast or as safe as a European car,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.58,0:58:16.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,but it offers everything the\NChinese motorist would want.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.96,0:58:20.92,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,There's lots of space in the\Nback, a couple of nice gadgets,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.03,0:58:26.30,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,wooden trim and enough headroom\Nfor anyone up to five foot three.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.36,0:58:33.00,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,The editor of a Chinese car\Nmagazine told me this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.04,0:58:37.29,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,that the Chinese like good\Nequipment in cars, good gadgets.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.39,0:58:39.48,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,And this actually does quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.52,0:58:44.07,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It has got sat-nav, incomprehensible\Nof course, reversing cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.11,0:58:47.54,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,decent audio system,\Nautomatic air-conditioning,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.58,0:58:50.72,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,audio controls on the steering wheel,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.76,0:58:54.83,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,digital dashboard... pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.14,0:59:01.10,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,I'd like to say that this\Nfeels like an old Alfa Romeo,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.14,0:59:05.32,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,but it doesn't really, chiefly\Nbecause of the automatic gearbox,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.36,0:59:09.31,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,which was made by a man who\NI think is a greengrocer.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.35,0:59:11.76,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Certainly, he has no comprehension
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.80,0:59:15.13,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,of what an automatic gearbox should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.17,0:59:19.69,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Stop changing gear! Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.87,0:59:23.85,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's all very well Jeremy whining\Nand shouting at his gearbox,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.90,0:59:25.42,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,but he should try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.45,0:59:28.44,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,This is a three-speed\Nautomatic with overdrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.57,0:59:32.10,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It's quite smooth, actually,\Nbut as a concept,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.14,0:59:35.32,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,it's just a tad old-fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.06,0:59:40.33,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,It is worth bearing in mind,\Nthough, that both these cars
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.39,0:59:43.63,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,cost £12,000, and that in China,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.72,0:59:47.62,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,a base model Audi A3 is\Nmore than twice that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.16,0:59:51.70,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,If you bear that price\Ndifference in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.90,0:59:55.74,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,and ignore the gearbox,\Nit's really not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.60,0:59:58.35,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Rides nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.39,1:00:00.32,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,CLUNK!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.36,1:00:03.48,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Most of the time. Er...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.52,1:00:07.25,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,At this point, we ran out of\Nthings... to say about our cars,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.29,1:00:09.97,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,so we met up for a discussion.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.66,1:00:16.09,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,So, James May, would you buy\Na Roewe 350 in Britain? No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.13,1:00:18.29,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,No. No. Would you buy a Trumpchi?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.64,1:00:22.47,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Only if it was very cheap.\NBut look at it this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.91,1:00:27.17,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,In just five years, China\Nhas gone from making that,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.52,1:00:31.25,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,whatever it is, to making these.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.29,1:00:33.39,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,With that rate of progress,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.50,1:00:36.21,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,where are they going to\Nbe in five years' time?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.27,1:00:38.64,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,That does take us back to\Nour original question...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.77,1:00:41.54,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,in five years' time,\Neverybody will be driving
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.54,1:00:44.31,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,Chinese cars... yes,\Nwe probably will.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.43,1:00:46.87,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,We are doomed. We are doomed.\NWe've absolutely...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.17,1:00:53.08,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,In the plums.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.99,1:01:26.96,제레미 대사,,0,0,0,,THEME TUNE PLAYED IN THE STYLE OF\NTRADITIONAL CHINESE MUSIC
